code: @Override protected LinksHandler getLinksHandler() {     return new WebMvcLinksHandler(). }

@Override @ResponseBody public Map<String, Map<String, Link>> links(HttpServletRequest request, HttpServletResponse response) {     return Collections.singletonMap("_links", WebMvcEndpointHandlerMapping.this.linksResolver.resolveLinks(request.getRequestURL().toString())). }
@Override public String toString() {     return "Actuator root web endpoint". }
